WEBVTT

00:01:57.435 --> 00:02:01.673
Mabadiliko yalikuja kwa Manson alipoamua kujifunza kusamehe

00:02:01.697 --> 00:02:03.447
kwa wale waliomuingiza jela.

00:02:05.784 --> 00:02:07.943
Naongea hilo likiwa ni ukweli.

00:02:08.776 --> 00:02:10.408
Kwa sababu namfahamu Manson.

00:02:12.403 --> 00:02:13.553
Mimi ni Manson.

00:02:14.546 --> 00:02:16.812
Jina langu halisi ni Peter Manson Ouko.

00:02:18.260 --> 00:02:19.783
Na baada ya hukumu yangu,

00:02:19.807 --> 00:02:22.207
baada ya kupata uamsho wa kusamehe,

00:02:23.318 --> 00:02:24.468
Nilisonga mbele

00:02:25.826 --> 00:02:27.269
katika kusaidia kubadili mfumo.

00:02:28.318 --> 00:02:31.182
Nilishaamua kwamba sitakuwa mhanga tena.